</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_86" id="41v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>err</ex>n</expan> Dyetrich Hofer czu
                            <expan>Sünching<ex>en</ex></expan>, pfleger czu Nocerbergk</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Dyetrich, als ir uns <add>bey <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Hansen
                  <expan>Maur<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>erm</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>,</add>
<expan>ges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Caspar
            Hertembergers, Wilhelm Czagreis, <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Edelmans und Hansen
                <expan>Snelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wegen, das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und also senden wir euch bey
                  dem<add><expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener</add> des <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>verczeih</add> brief, als ir uns <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, und <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> auch das
            durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> und des <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Caspar Hertembergers wegen also
              <expan>aufneme<ex>n</ex></expan> und wir biten <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleisziklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <add>daz ir uns den gegen brief, den euch
                  <expan>de<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurtt, von dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Caspar <expan>Hertenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sigelt</expan> schicken und in auch</add> daran weisen wöllet, daz
            er im fürbaz die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gütliche<ex>n</ex></expan> lasse <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein. Das
                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan> ümb ew und in
                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
